%%{init: {'theme': 'base', 'themeVariables': { 'fontSize': '14px' }}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User Query
    participant SF as Snowflake Engine
    participant POL as Masking Policy
    participant DATA as Table Data

    User->>SF: SELECT email FROM customers
    SF->>POL: Check CURRENT_ROLE()
    
    alt Role = DATA_ADMIN
        POL->>SF: Return original value
        SF->>User: alice@company.com
    else Role = DATA_ANALYST
        POL->>SF: Apply mask function
        SF->>User: ****@company.com
    else Role = BUSINESS_USER
        POL->>SF: Full redaction
        SF->>User: [REDACTED]
    end

    Note over DATA: Original data is NEVER modified<br/>Masking happens at query time
